#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate Game Controller"
msgstr "Umerjanje igralnega krmilnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module provides an interface to calibrate your game controller as well "
"as see which functions on your game controller are mapped to which logical "
"button or axis."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul zagotavlja vmesnik za umerjanje igralnega krmilnika in prikaz "
"funkcij igralnega krmilnika, ki so prirejene posameznim logičnim gumbom ali "
"osem."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the game controller module"
msgstr "Tu je posnetek zaslona modula igralnega krmilnika"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "The game controller module"
msgstr "Modul igralnega krmilnika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Device"
msgstr "Naprava"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can see the logical location of the device. If you have more than "
"one game controller, you can also select which one to configure."
msgstr ""
"Tu si lahko ogledate logično lokacijo naprave. Če imate več igralnih "
"krmilnikov, lahko izberete tudi enega, ki ga želite konfigurirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no game controller is automatically found on your computer and you know "
"that there is one attached, you can enter the correct device file here."
msgstr ""
"Če v računalniku ni samodejno najden noben igralni krmilnik, vi pa veste, da "
"je priključen, lahko tukaj vnesete pravilno datoteko naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position"
msgstr "Položaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plotted location of the X and Y axes of the game controller's joystick. "
"Enable <guibutton>Show trace</guibutton> to plot the path of the joystick "
"from one point to another."
msgstr ""
"Izrisana lokacija osi X in Y krmilne palice igralnega krmilnika. Omogočite "
"<guibutton>Pokaži sled</guibutton> za izris poti krmilne palice od ene točke "
"do druge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the joystick cannot reach every point on this graph, or if it does not "
"center correctly, you need to calibrate your device."
msgstr ""
"Če krmilna palica ne doseže vseh točk na tem grafu ali če se ne osredotoči "
"pravilno, morate napravo umeriti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A place to see the pressed state of buttons on your game controller and if "
"the buttons are mapped correctly. When a button is pressed, "
"<guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel> will appear next to the logical number (as the "
"computer sees it) of the button which was pressed."
msgstr ""
"Mesto za prikaz stanja pritisnjenih gumbov na igralnem krmilniku in "
"preveritev, ali so gumbi pravilno preslikani. Ko je gumb pritisnjen, se ob "
"logični številki (kot jo vidi računalnik) gumba, ki je bil pritisnjen, "
"pojavi <guilabel>PRESSED</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Axes"
msgstr "Osi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the numerical values of the axis positions. 0 is centered and "
"the maximum and minimum values depend on the game controller and the "
"particular axis."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže številčne vrednosti položajev osi. 0 je v središču, največja in "
"najmanjša vrednost pa sta odvisni od igralnega krmilnika in posamezne osi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calibrate"
msgstr "Umeri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on <guibutton>Calibrate</guibutton> will open a dialog to calibrate "
"every axis on your joysticks."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na <guibutton>Kalibriraj</guibutton> se odpre pogovorno okno za "
"kalibracijo vseh osi na igralnih palicah."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Calibrating your game controller</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Umerjanje igralnega krmilnika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Calibrating your game controller</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Umerjanje igralnega krmilnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each axis will have to be moved to the minimum position, then the center, "
"and finally the maximum position. A meter in the bottom left corner of the "
"dialog will help determine which way increases and which way decreases the "
"values."
msgstr ""
"Vsako os bo treba premakniti v najmanjši položaj, nato v središče in "
"nazadnje v največji položaj. Merilnik v spodnjem levem kotu pogovornega okna "
"vam bo pomagal določiti, v katero smer se vrednosti povečajo in v katero "
"zmanjšajo."
